Detailed Description

The storage container type of drpttracer's output. This data struct is used by drpttracer to store PT metadata, PT trace, and sideband data. These data can be dumped into different files by the caller. These files can be the inputs of pt2ir_t, which decodes the PT data into Dynamorio's IR.
